!!!Solid2             1-30     6-21
END

BOUNDARY_CONDITIONS
!!!Y_begin   FractureInlet   Flux
!!!Y_end     Solid2   Flux
!!!X_begin   Solid2   Flux
!!!X_end     Solid2   Flux

